OL,7,FPeople classed as Lockerbie bombing
OL,8,Fvictims are being urged to register
OL,9,Ffor access to court proceedings ahead
OL,10,Fof next year's US trial.
OL,12,FThe bombing of Pan Am flight 103,
OL,13,Ftravelling from London to New York on
OL,14,F21 December 1988, killed 270 people in
OL,15,FBritain's largest terrorist atrocity.
