OL,7,FLibyan-born Abu Agila Mohammad Mas'ud
OL,8,FKheir Al-Marimi accused of being the
OL,9,Fbomb maker in the Lockerbie terrorist
OL,10,Fattack will appear in federal court
OL,11,FWashington in May 2025. He denies all
OL,12,Fcharges.
OL,14,FThe US Congress has passed legislation
OL,15,Fto make online access to court
OL,16,Fproceedings available to victims.
