OL,7,FPan Am flight 103 Lockerbie Legacy
OL,8,FFoundation says around 100 people have
OL,9,Fregistered, but they believe more
OL,10,Fshould be applying before the deadline
OL,11,Fof 9 October 2024.
OL,13,FIan McLatchie said: "So far we believe
OL,14,Fthere's only around 100 people, but
OL,15,Fpotentially there's thousands of
OL,16,Fvictims.
