OL,7,F"The families, the first responders...
OL,8,Fthey are all entitled to be on there,
OL,9,Fthey need to register to be part of
OL,10,Fthis remote access for the trial next
OL,11,FMay. Who knows, there could be a
OL,12,Fchance of compensation out there, but
OL,13,Fthey must be registered."
OL,15,FMike Thomson, a retired police
OL,16,Finspector who volunteers at the
OL,17,Fremembrance room at Tundergarth
OL,18,FChurch, says the Lockerbie terrorist
OL,19,Fattack has become 'a major part' of
OL,20,Fhis life.
