OL,7,FHe said: "I don't know anybody who I
OL,8,Fworked alongside with who would deny
OL,9,Fthat they hadn't been emotionally
OL,10,Faffected by it. You can deny stuff,
OL,11,Fsuppress feelings and memories that
OL,12,Fyou have. I think you have to do that
OL,13,Fat a stage to get on with your life,
OL,14,Fbut it's still there, it's under the
OL,15,Fsurface."
OL,17,FMike was a 22-year-old police officer
OL,18,Fwhen the Lockerbie bombing happened 36
OL,19,Fyears ago. He believes it is important
OL,20,Ffor victims to register before the
OL,21,Fdeadline next week.
