OL,7,FHe added: "I think it's a healthy
OL,8,Fthing to do, and I also think by
OL,9,Fsigning up and registering as I have
OL,10,Fdone as a living victim, it provides
OL,11,Fsupport to others and encourages
OL,12,Fothers to come forward."
OL,14,FVisitors from around the world attend
OL,15,Fthe Lockerbie memorial, located at
OL,16,FTundergarth Church, to pay tribute to
OL,17,Fthe victims.
