OL,7,FWill Lester, visiting the memorial
OL,8,Fwith his family from California, said:
OL,9,F"This is our first time in the UK and
OL,10,Fhaving experienced 9/11, this was on
OL,11,Four way heading up to the Isle of
OL,12,FSkye, I just wanted to come and pay my
OL,13,Frespects to the victims of 1988, to
OL,14,Ftheir terrorist attack here."
